The concierge was very friendly and helpful.	Rooms are very nice and clean.	The buffet breakfast, which is included in the tariff, was very good.	Staff were all very professional and helpful.	The breakfast buffet was excellent.	Excellent 5 star hotel in Rome, the location is great.	The staff was friendly, multi-lingual and very attentive to the guests needs.	The room was nice and spacious, no views as it is in a street.	We enjoyed our stay at this hotel.	We only had one day in Rome and the location of this hotel was perfect.